article.title: Wisconsin Export Resource Directory
article.summary: Learn more about Wisconsin agencies, associates, and resources that assist Wisconsin companies increase their exports.
article.content:
​This Wisconsin Export Resource directory provides links to Wisconsin agencies, associates, and resources that assist Wisconsin companies increase their exports. Click each category to contact business providing export services to Wisconsin companies.

  • State of Wisconsin Agencies
  • Wisconsin Industry Associations
  • Wisconsin Trade Associations
  • Wisconsin Native American Governments
  • Wisconsin Small Business Development Center
  • Wisconsin Congressional Districts
  • Wisconsin Chambers of Commerce
  • Wisconsin Women's Business Initiative
  • Northwest Wisconsin Manufacturing Outreach Center
  • Milwaukee Urban League​
